    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to check out my car. I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty\u2014it\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in really wonderful shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road for its next big adventure. Whether you're commuting or heading out for a weekend getaway, this car is a total champ and runs like a dream. I\u2019m looking for a good home for it, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin. Can't wait to hear from you!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
