      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, powered by the high-strung S54B32 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system. This example features the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission, providing a direct mechanical connection to the rear-mounted M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed with a firm subframe and refreshed bushings, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry performs as intended. Preventative maintenance is up to date, including a comprehensive VANOS service and rod bearing inspection. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain is dialed and the 8,000 RPM redline remains as intoxicating as ever. A driver-focused machine for the true purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. Minor exterior wear. Runs smoothly. Clean title.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride of ownership, offering a reliable and refined driving experience. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, and while you will find a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper from daily use, the body remains straight and free of any significant dents. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and smoke-free. The leather upholstery is in great shape, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s seat, and the original carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. Every button, switch, and digital display functions perfectly, including the ice-cold A/C and the premium audio system. Under the hood, the engine is dry and runs smoothly, backed by a complete service history showing regular oil changes and preventative maintenance. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a solid, honest car that bridges the gap between a daily driver and a collector's piece, ready for the road with no immediate work required.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
