    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a distinguished balance of performance and value. Meticulously maintained and presenting in commendable condition, it offers a refined driving experience for the discerning owner. Every component has been rigorously inspected to ensure mechanical integrity, providing a reliable and sophisticated transport solution. We invite you to acquire this exceptional example of engineering excellence.",
