      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolute gold to own. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape\u2014super reliable, clean, and runs like a dream! It\u2019s been well-loved and is totally ready for a new owner to take it on some fresh adventures. If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks sharp and drives smooth, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions or come by to see it in person!",
      "price": 32500.0,
